      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALL DRESSED UP (1) was in the money last start when second in a Grade 5 in 21.57, clocking one of the quickest times on the card and a personal best this course and distance as well. Happy to have her on top here. BOOM TOWN (5) goes very well this course and distance starting 10 times for five wins and four minors. Comes off a (19.22) win last time, scoring by 5.5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 352m at this track. Suited here and expected to run well. SHIMA POLLY (8) is an accomplished sprinter with a great record at the short dashes. Finished fourth latest over 390m at this track (22.16) in a Grade 4/5. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Key runner on best form. TIPPY TOE (2) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
